+================================================================+
| PebbleWasher v0.0                                              |
|----------------------------------------------------------------|
| Author: Crwire                                                 |
| Created: 24 June 2014                                          |
| Updated: 24 June 2014                                          |
+================================================================+

This app is written in C for the Pebble SmartWatch for the purposes of feeding accelerometer data from the watch to a companion mobile application. 

Ultimately this allows the companion application to detect a handwashing motion.

+================================================================+
| CHANGELOG                                                      |
+================================================================+
v0-0
Project initialised and ready for when I receive a Pebble to start developing on.

